tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE 3d_printing_machine_utilization (
  machine_id UUID,
  utilization_rate FLOAT,
  printing_time TIMESTAMP,
  material_used VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE 3d_printing_jobs (
    job_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    machine_id UUID,
    start_time TIMESTAMP,
    end_time TIMESTAMP,
    material_used VARCHAR(50),
    job_status VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE 3d_printing_machine (
  machine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
  model VARCHAR(255),
  purchase_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE print_job (
  job_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  start_time TIMESTAMP,
  end_time TIMESTAMP,
  quantity INT,
  material VARCHAR(255),
  machine_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (machine_id) REFERENCES 3d_printing_machine(machine_id)
);

CREATE TABLE 3d_printing_jobs (
    job_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    printer_id INT,
    job_type TEXT,
    material_type TEXT,
    job_start_time TIMESTAMP,
    job_end_time TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE MaintenanceLogs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    machine_id INT,
    maintenance_type VARCHAR(50),
    maintenance_date DATE,
    technician_name VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE PrintJobLogs (
    job_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    machine_id INT,
    job_name VARCHAR(50),
    job_duration FLOAT,
    filament_used FLOAT
);
